window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is the last three books in this six-book series.</p> <p>In a world where monsters and humans struggle to coexist, Alex thought he had everything under control. With his loyal lovers Leeha and Bridget by his side, they navigated the turbulent waters of Boromour. But then, Sara enters the picture, a wild catgirl who is determined to prove her worth to the group.</p> <p>As they try to make sense of their complicated relationships, Alex discovers that the world is more complicated than he ever imagined. God, the ruler of their world, has a plan for everyone, but not everyone is content to follow blindly. The angels, who are supposed to be the workforce of God, are starting to question their role in the grand scheme of things.</p> <p>Alex and his group find themselves in the middle of a brewing conflict, one that threatens to shatter the delicate balance of Boromour. With monsters and angels pitted against each other, Alex must fight to gain freedom for the planet he loves.</p> <p>But freedom comes with a cost, and Alex is about to discover that the price might be too high. As he delves deeper into the mysteries of his world, he finds himself facing off against monsters, angels, and even God himself. But with his loyal companions by his side, Alex is ready to take on whatever challenges come his way.</p> <p>Join Alex and his girls as they fight for what they believe in, in a world where nothing is as it seems. With danger lurking around every corner, they must rely on their wits, strength, and love to survive. Will they emerge victorious, or will they fall in the face of overwhelming odds? Only time will tell in this epic adventure.</p>"; 
